<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>This privacy policy is not to be taken seriously, it serves only to compliment the page.</p>

<p> 

<h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
    When you use our website, we may collect the following types of information:<br />
    -Personal Information: such as your name, email address, phone number, payment information, and government ID (for identity verification).<br />
    -Booking Information: details about your reservations, travel dates, and preferences.<br />
    -Communication: messages between hosts and guests, support tickets, and reviews.<br />
    -Usage Data: IP address, browser type, device information, and pages visited.<br />

<h3>2. How We Use Your Information </h3>
    We use the information we collect to:<br />
    -Process bookings and payments.<br />
    -Connect guests with hosts.<br />
    -Verify user identities and ensure safety.<br />
    -Provide customer support.<br />
    -Improve our website and user experience.<br />
    -Send important updates and promotional offers (with your consent).<br />

<h3>3. Sharing Your Information</h3>
    We may share your information with:<br />
    -Hosts or Guests: for completing bookings.<br />
    -Service Providers: like payment processors or background check services.<br />
    -Legal Authorities: if required by law or to protect our rights and users.<br />
    -We do not sell your personal information.<br />

<h3>4. Cookies and Tracking</h3>
    We use cookies and similar technologies to:<br />
    -Remember your preferences.<br />
    -Analyze site traffic and performance.<br />
    -Customize your experience.<br />

    You can manage cookies through your browser settings.<br />

<h3>5. Data Security</h3>
    We take reasonable measures to protect your personal data. However, no online service is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.<br />

<h3>6. Your Rights</h3>
    Depending on your location, you may have the right to:<br />
    -Access or correct your personal information.<br />
    -Delete your account.<br />
    -Opt out of marketing emails.<br />

<h3>7. Changes to This Policy</h3>
    We may update this policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new effective date.<br />

</p>
